metadata_description: The BackDoor of HIPHP gives you the power to control websites based on PHP using HTTP/HTTPS protocol. By sending files - tokens and commands through port 80s POST/GET method - users can access a range of activities such as downloading and editing files. It also allows for connecting to Tor networks with password protection for extra security.
